# ============================================================
# .gitignore — keeps internal docs OUT of the public site.
# These folders stay on your computer; they just stop being
# committed and served by GitHub Pages.
# Added June 2026 during security cleanup (P0).
# ============================================================

# Internal strategy, planning, and agent docs
_dev/
_reports/
_archive/
_database/
_myjourney/
myintern/briefs/
manamana_tickets_v2.md

# Backup files
*.bak

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Node tooling (e.g. local test deps — never part of the site)
node_modules/
package-lock.json
